16
00:00:43,770 --> 00:00:44,560
Otherwise,

17
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:46,380
this will be our last time

18
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:47,280
seeing this palace's

19
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:48,430
magnificent splendor.

20
00:00:48,730 --> 00:00:49,750
Man proposes,

21
00:00:50,970 --> 00:00:52,120
Heaven disposes.

22
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:53,600
Your Highness,

23
00:00:53,700 --> 00:00:55,020
Shang Kefeng's men are coming to kill us.

24
00:00:55,050 --> 00:00:56,570
